court: IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICATURE AT BOMBAY
judgment_text:
IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICATURE AT BOMBAY

ORDINARY ORIGINAL CIVIL JURISDICTION

SUIT NO. 345 of 1984

Gwalior Oil Mills

.. Plaintiff

versus

Kotak & CO. & Ors.

.. Defendants

...

Mr.Viral Amin i/b M/s.B. Amin & CO. for plaintiff.

Mr.Murtaza Ali i/b Law Charter for the defendants.

CORAM : D.G. KARNIK, J

DATED : 15th July 2005. P.C. P.C. P.C.

. Heard learned counsel for the parties. The

defendants have not filed the written statement for

nearly 20 years. The suit is for recovery of

money. Hence, suit of the plaintiff is decreed in

terms of prayer clauses (a) and (b).

D.G.KARNIK,, J
